headline.print_headline: Canada's OMERS Ventures to More Than Double Tech Investing: CEO
headline.main: Canada's OMERS Ventures to More Than Double Tech Investing: CEO

lead_paragraph: The venture capital arm of one of Canada's largest pension funds is raising a second, larger round of funding to invest in Canadian technology startups, its chief executive said on Thursday.
